longBusinessSummary: Yünsa Yünlü Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. engages in the manufacture and sale of woolen textile products in Turkey. It operates through Textile and Apparel segments. The company offers wool and blended fabrics, including men's woolen and worsted, trousers, and jackets fabrics; women's, fashion trend and clothing fabrics; corporate wear fabrics; and upholstery fabrics primarily used in commercial vehicle industry. It also exports its products to approximately 50 countries. The company was incorporated in 1973 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey. Yünsa Yünlü Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. is a subsidiary of Sürmegöz Tekstil Yatirim A.S.
